recent_articles.title: Microsoft says its AI diagnoses patients more accurately than doctors
recent_articles.summary:
New research finds that AI-driven diagnostic tools may be more effective than human medical workers when it comes to accurate diagnosis. Microsoft (MSFT) AI Diagnostic Orchestrator (MAI-DxO) correctly diagnosed up to 85% of cases, an accuracy rate more than four times that of a group of experienced physicians.

Microsoft AI CEO Mustafa Suleyman joins Opening Bid with Yahoo Finance Executive Editor Brian Sozzi to discuss the findings of the report and the role of AI in the future of medical diagnostic testing analysis.
